title: Beyond the Curtain of Space: Chapter I
description: Professor Newton, a brilliant scientist, has broken all ties with the Federation and taken up residence on the alien world of Ophesia. Vena Ray convinces Commissioner Drake that the professor is not a traitor, but is being held against his will. Drake orders Rocky, Winkie and Vena to fly to Ophesia, fake a forced landing and find out whether the Professor is really friend or foe.
